## Quick Start

```bash
# Frontend setup
cd web && npm install && npm run build && cd ..
go mod tidy

# Dev mode (frontend build + Go server)
.\scripts\dev.ps1

# Build (outputs to deploy/linux, deploy/windows)
.\scripts\build.ps1
```

## Architecture

| Layer | Technology | Notes |
|-------|-----------|-------|
| Frontend | React + TypeScript | Vite build |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS | Utility-first |
| UI Components | shadcn/ui | Radix-based, `npx shadcn@latest add <component>` |
| Backend | Go (Golang) | net/http router + API server |
| Database | SQLite (modernc.org/sqlite) | CGo-free, WAL mode, `data/app.db` |
| Deploy | Go single binary | React build → go:embed → single executable |

## Adding shadcn/ui Components

```bash
cd web
npx shadcn@latest add card
npx shadcn@latest add dialog
npx shadcn@latest add input
```

Components are added to `web/src/components/ui/`.

